      <title>美元成为本周市场混乱的最新受害者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/dollar-emerges-as-latest-victim-of-this-week-s-markets-mayhem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日益严重的全球贸易战争威胁到美国的经济增长，因此美元成为本周市场动荡的最新受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/dollar-emerges-as-latest-victim-of-this-week-s-markets-mayhem</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 01:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔在最小的日本交易中出售6.28亿美元的日元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/berkshire-sells-628-million-in-yen-bonds-in-smallest-japan-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔·海瑟薇公司（Berkshire Hathaway Inc.）周五的债券为900亿日元（6.28亿美元），即使急剧的市场波动促使几家日本公司取消了销售额，也完成了日元交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/berkshire-sells-628-million-in-yen-bonds-in-smallest-japan-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 00:59:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油的抛售会随着贸易战争的速度加快速度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）激进的贸易政策触发的全球市场上的越来越多的障碍，石油引发了人们对经济衰退和风险飞行的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票延长下降，美元落在关税困境上：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票和债券在三年来最大的暴跌后，股票和债券恢复了抛售，由于全球贸易战争恶化，股票损失损失，这已经侵蚀了已经脆弱的风险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股票简历下降，因为美国 - 中国贸易紧张局势加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/japanese-stocks-set-to-resume-slide-on-us-china-trade-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股票恢复了关注，因为世界上两个最大经济体之间的贸易战不断升级将减缓全球增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/japanese-stocks-set-to-resume-slide-on-us-china-trade-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:34:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场上的关税障碍燃料出埃及美国资产的市场暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/markets-plummet-as-tariff-war-woes-fuel-exodus-from-us-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统在他曾经是世纪的贸易战中回溯不到24小时以防止金融市场的崩溃，疯狂的抛售又击中了美国股票，债券和美元，因为担心全球衰退的华尔街。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/markets-plummet-as-tariff-war-woes-fuel-exodus-from-us-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 20:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CATL获得了今年最大清单的香港批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/china-ev-battery-maker-catl-gets-approval-for-hk-listing-ifr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电动汽车电池制造商当代Amperex Technology Co. Ltd.赢得了香港的批准，可以继续在该市上市，该公司可能至少获得50亿美元，这可能是今年全球最大的产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/china-ev-battery-maker-catl-gets-approval-for-hk-listing-ifr</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 11:37:38 GMT</pubDate>
